summary: Adds a weaponry with 8 mannequins and more. Can be found by using a trapdoor in Delphine\'s secret room.
descriptionHtml:
Adds a weaponry with 8 mannequins and more. Can be found by using a trapdoor in Delphine\'s secret room.
Features
--------------------------
Eight mannequins.
Twenty two weapon racks
One weapon plaque
A forge
A workbench
A grindstone
A tanning rack
An alchemy lab
An arcane enchanter
Misc items
---------------------------
Can be found in Delphine\'s Secret room. Just take the trapdoor.
author: KoZAcK1021
